commentTextItems.html: full and on the off, Jacobs waits on it and flicks through midwicket in  fine style and that is the end of the game, cracking finish that

commentPostTextItems.html: That is the end of a superb match. With this result West Indies go through to the finla where India are waiting for them
Join us again on July 4 for the last remaining league match in this series. India match up with West Indies in a rehearsal of the final
Till then it's a very good night to you all from the CricInfo team
Mail all your feedback to comms@cricinfo.com as always

commentTextItems.html: full and on the toes, attempted yorker, flicked to midwicket, quick single stolen
full and outside the off, played back past streak to long off
back of a length and outside the off, played down with soft hands, quick single scampered, all panic here as Streak dives throws at the stumps, the batsman too dives in~
overpitched and outside the off,m big swing and a miss, 5 off 5 now
back of a length and outside the off, driven through covers

commentPostTextItems.html: 5 to win off the last over

stories.title: West Indies win by five wickets to clinch spot in Coca-Cola Cup final
stories.summary:
Zimbabwe entered their final match in the first round of their
inaugural triangular tournament knowing they had to beat West Indies
handsomely, and then have India beat West Indies in Wednesday's match,
to reach the final
